# Research Result

**Goal:** Find the correct general formula for η(C_p³) (the short Davenport constant for rank-3 elementary p-groups). Known: η(C_2³)=8, η(C_3³)=17, η(C_5³)=33. The formula 8(p-1)+1 fits p=3,5 but may fail for p≥7. Compute η(C_7³) to test. Then identify the correct formula and prove it (or prove it for specific primes). If no clean closed form exists, characterize the growth rate and structural regime changes.
